tafsir[29]{c,v,t}:
  37,154,"Ko he…ďi on, onon …ďee sirkoo…ďe, hi…óon √Īaawira ndee √Īaaaworaa oo√Īiinde, wa…óanon Alla …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe, su…ďao…óon hoore-mon wor…ďe …ďen?"
  37,155,"E on miijitotaako wonnde ko e meere won…óon e mun? Tawde si on taskike, on yi'iray non bonnde fi…ďnde mon nden."
  37,156,"Kaa hi…óon jogii hujja e dalil …ďanngir…óo Deftere maa Nulaa…óo?"
  37,157,"Haray addee deftere mon ka hujja mon on woni …óon, si wonii ko on goongu…ďe e haala!"
  37,158,"Sirkoo…ďe …ďen wa…ói hakkunde Allah e Malaa'ika'en, asko dammbe, …óum ko ko …ďe aa∆īinoo wonnde Malaa'ika'en, ko …ďi…ó…ďe Allah rew…ďe! Hara non, …ďen Malaa'ikaa…ďe no anndi, pellet, Alla tawnoyay …ďen sirkoo…ďe, e hasboore nden."
  37,159,"Allah senike O laa…ďii, gaay e kon sirkoo…ďe …ďen sifotoo, dammbude Mo …ďi…ó…óo e genndiraawo, ekw immorde e ka yahdaa e Makko!"
  37,160,"Si wanaa jeyaa…ďe Allah, la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen. ∆Āen …óon sifortaa Allah, ko yahdaani e Makko."
  37,161,"Anndon onon …ďee sirkoo…ďe, e ko rewoton kon gaanin Allah."
  37,162,"On wonaali majjiniroo…ďe kon ko rewoton, wo…ó…ďe goo e diine goonga."
  37,163,"Si wanaa on mo Allah winndani naatugol ka Yiite. On …óon yeddiray sa…ďu …óum, o naata nge. Onon non, e rewetee…ói mon …óin, on alaa nden feere."
  37,164,"Malaa'ika'en …ďanngini jeyeede ma…ď…ďe ka Allah, da…óndinoo e ko sirkoo…ďe …ďen aa∆īori…ďe kon, wi'ugol: Alaa e amen, mo alanaa …óum, darorde anndaande, fii rewugol Alla …óoftoo Mo."
  37,165,"Menen Malaa'ika, ko men darnaa…ďe saffinaa, fii rewugol Allah …óoftoo Mo. Ko memen kadi woni subbunhinantoo…ďe Allah …ďen, sifaaji yahdu…ói e Makko."
  37,166,"Menen Malaa'ika, ko men darnaa…ďe saffinaa, fii rewugol Allah …óoftoo Mo. Ko memen kadi woni seninoo…ďe Allah ko O haandaani ko sifaaji."
  37,167,"Sirkoo…ďe Makkah …ďen woniino e wi'ugol, ado nuleede Muhammadu (yo o his): Sinno hara me…óen joginoo Deftere sugu Defte arane …óen, wano Tawreeta, ko pellet, men la…ď…ďinanayno Alla dewalngal. Hara non, ko e fenaande …ďe woni. Tawde Muhammadu addanii …ďe Alqur'aana, …ďe yeddi nde. Kono non, aray nde …ďe anndata, fii lepte sa…ótu…óe, ha…ď…ďii…óe …ďe …óen, √Ďalnde Darngal."
  37,168,""
