  37,170,""
  37,171,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, wonnde ko …ďe wallirtee…ďe e hoore ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, hujja e dolle …óe Alla neeminiri …ďe. E wonnde poolal ngal, ko fii konu Amen, ha…ďirayngu fii Alla ngun, no daalol Alla ngol …ďamtora."
  37,172,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, wonnde pellet, ko …ďe wallirtee…ďe e hoore ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, hujja e dolle …óe Alla neeminiri …ďe. E wonnde poolal ngal, ko fii konu Amen, ha…ďirayngu fii Alla ngun, no daalol Alla ngol …ďamtora."
  37,173,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, wonnde ko …ďe wallirtee…ďe e hoore ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, hujja e dolle …óe Alla neeminiri …ďe. E wonnde poolal ngal, ko fii konu Amen, ha…ďirayngu fii Alla ngun, no daalol Alla ngol …ďamtora."
  37,174,"An Nulaa…óo, …óuurno …ďee sirkoo…ďe sa…óta feeree…ďe, haa e saanga nde Allah humpitu maa, arugol lepte ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  37,175,"Ndaaraa …ďe, tuma lepte …óen jippotoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe aray yi'ude, ka yi'ugol nafataa …ďe!"
  37,176,"E hara ko lepte Alla …óen, …ďee sirkoo…ďe he√Īorta?"
  37,177,"Si lepte Allah …óen jippike e ma…ď…ďe, haray bimmbi ma…ď…ďe on bonii !"
  37,178,"An Nulaa…óo, …óuurno e ma…ď…ďe, haa Allah √Īaawa fii leptugol …ďe ngol."
  37,179,"Ndaaraa; kam…ďe kadi, …ďe aray yi'ude lepte Allah …óen yanooje e ma…ď…ďe."
  37,180,"Senayee woodanii Joomi maa, an Muhammadu, O laa…ďii e kon ko sirkoo…ďe …ďen siforta Mo e ustii…ói !"
  37,181,"Kisiyee Allah e mantoore Makko, wonii e Nulaa…ďe Makko teddu…ďe …ďen."
  37,182,"Yettoore nden fow, woodanii Alla senii…óo toowu…óo On. Ko Kanko hanndi e …óum. Ko Kanko woni Jey…óo winndere nden fow. Jey…óo …óum alaa, si wanaa Kanko."